From 67903f2baf4938fe9609714411f04d2456b234f6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "v.oleynikov" <vasily.oleynikov@flant.com>
Date: Tue, 12 May 2026 13:48:20 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add VSC-only snapshot model support

This patch enables external-snapshotter to operate on VolumeSnapshotContent
without a corresponding VolumeSnapshot.

It allows internal Deckhouse controllers (e.g. storage-foundation VCR/VRR)
to drive CSI snapshot and restore operations using service-level APIs
without exposing VolumeSnapshot resources to user namespaces.

The change is backward-compatible and preserves existing behavior for
legacy VolumeSnapshot-based workflows.
